{"about_the_game":"Become a giant walking dice and battle to the end of an ever-changing dungeon! Can you escape the cruel whims of Lady Luck? Now featuring &quot;Dicey Dungeons: Reunion&quot;, a free DLC with six brand-new episodes! (Check out the Reunion OST on Bandcamp!)<br><br>In this fast-paced deckbuilding roguelike from Terry Cavanagh (Super Hexagon, VVVVVV), Chipzel, and Marlowe Dobbe, you'll fight monsters, find better loot, level up your heroes, and maybe even take down the Goddess of Fortune, Lady Luck herself. Balance your carefully planned strategies against the unknown of a dice roll.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/861540/extras/aboutgame_chars.gif?t=1661358070\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/861540/extras/contestants.png?t=1661358070\" /><br>Play as six different characters, each with their own unique play styles and abilities.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Thief, who steals random enemy equipment every turn!<br></li><li>The Robot, who gains dice by playing a push-your-luck blackjack game!<br></li><li>The Inventor, overcome with inspiration, who must destroy their own equipment after each fight to get parts for powerful new gadgets!<br></li><li>and more!</li></ul><br>Master each class and figure out which one best fits your style in this charming world filled with a growing array of twists and secrets.<br><br>Can you make it out alive? Maybe, but luck is definitely not on your side.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/861540/extras/Aboutgame_Monsters.gif?t=1661358070\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/861540/extras/features.png?t=1661358070\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Six wildly different playable classes: Warrior, Thief, Robot, Jester, Inventor and Witch.<br></li><li>Dozens of enemies, ranging from Vacuum Cleaners that want to suck your blood, to creatures from Irish mythology, to suave malevolent snowmen.<br></li><li>A catchy, upbeat and energetic soundtrack by Chipzel (previously, the musician from Super Hexagon).<br></li><li>Beautiful and adorable artwork by Marlowe Dobbe.<br></li><li>Procedurally generated for endless play-throughs.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unlock episodes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/ffb9213a9d27f1eedbb6da47f62adb45692d4a60.jpg"},{"name":"6 episodes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/b2e597e4d8bd6cd7d59f0379faa154a3620779ad.jpg"},{"name":"9 episodes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/088651ff28c88283bb97b00fe009ccae6999d56f.jpg"},{"name":"12 episodes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/0c03247ce586fd6804b9b77290dbfca1ad847a47.jpg"},{"name":"All episodes for one contestant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/a575329193feb4475adc9795acf9a78f2535c0bb.jpg"},{"name":"Curse of Greed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/39ca5c15df23073338405fba6a358356d29e2748.jpg"},{"name":"Finders Keepers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/d987369dc1f2e8e38ec96fbba870ac47c314b8b2.jpg"},{"name":"You Choose, You Lose","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/9965fed543f77814177edf1d10dc578823711c7b.jpg"},{"name":"The Inevitability of Rust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/66d877ad6b54c3bc8e7fc6d2b603bf5852107302.jpg"},{"name":"Countdown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/861540/a4314976020c9ff3f29c9a153edbef44798477bf.jpg"}],"to